        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="安装visual-studio-code"><a href="#安装visual-studio-code" class="headerlink" title="安装visual studio code"></a>安装visual studio code</h2><ul><li><p>扩展商店搜索<code>live server</code>安装实时重载插件</p></li><li><p>扩展商店搜索<code>chinese</code>即可安装简体中文包，重启<code>vscode</code>即生效</p></li><li><p>输入<code>!</code>，然后按下<code>tab</code>键，<code>vscode</code>会自动创建一个空的网页模板，如图：</p></li></ul><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://gitee.com/gahotx/blogimage/raw/master/image-20210220200709354.png"></p><h2 id="HTML最基础的标签"><a href="#HTML最基础的标签" class="headerlink" title="HTML最基础的标签"></a>HTML最基础的标签</h2><ul><li><code>html</code>文件必须有的标签：<code>&lt;html&gt;</code>、<code>&lt;head&gt;</code>、<code>&lt;title&gt;</code>、<code>&lt;body&gt;</code></li><li><code>&lt;title&gt;</code>：网页显示的标题</li><li><code>&lt;h1~h6&gt;</code>：标题</li><li><code>&lt;p&gt;</code>：段落，每个字符之间不管有多少个回车或者空格，网页中显示都是一个空格隔开</li><li><code>&lt;br&gt;</code>：换行</li><li><code>&lt;strong&gt;</code>：字体加粗</li><li><code>&lt;em&gt;</code>：字体斜体</li><li><code>&lt;button&gt;</code>：按钮</li><li><code>&lt;li&gt;</code>：列表项</li><li><code>&lt;ul&gt;</code>：无序列表</li><li><code>&lt;ol&gt;</code>：有序列表</li></ul><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://gitee.com/gahotx/blogimage/raw/master/image-20210220204904403.png"></p><h2 id="初见CSS"><a href="#初见CSS" class="headerlink" title="初见CSS"></a>初见CSS</h2><ul><li><code>CSS</code>由<code>选择器</code>，<code>属性</code>，<code>值</code>构成，如下：</li></ul><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">style</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    selector &#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="css">        property: value;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="css">        property2: value;</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">style</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>常见<code>property</code>如下：</li></ul><p><code>color</code>：颜色 </p><p><code>background</code> ：背景</p><p><code>font-family</code>：字体</p><p><code>opacity</code>：透明度</p><p><code>border</code>：边框</p><p><code>border-radius</code>：圆角边框</p><h2 id="常见块标签"><a href="#常见块标签" class="headerlink" title="常见块标签"></a>常见块标签</h2><ul><li><p><code>div</code>、<code>header</code>、<code>section</code>、<code>footer</code> </p></li><li><p>新学的<code>property</code>：<code>margin</code>（外边距）、<code>padding</code>（内边距），设置值顺序为顺时针（<code>上右下左</code>）</p></li></ul><h2 id="flex布局大法"><a href="#flex布局大法" class="headerlink" title="flex布局大法"></a>flex布局大法</h2><ul><li>把列项变成同行，弹性变化</li></ul><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">display: flex;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">flex-direction: row;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>把<code>ul</code>无序列表前的·去掉</li></ul><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">list-style-type: none;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>把<code>li</code>列项变成内联块</li></ul><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">display: inline-block;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="多页面间的跳转"><a href="#多页面间的跳转" class="headerlink" title="多页面间的跳转"></a>多页面间的跳转</h2><ul><li><code>a</code>标签超链接格式</li></ul><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">a</span> <span class="attr">href</span>=<span class="string">&quot;url&quot;</span>&gt;</span>&quot;name&quot;<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">a</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><code>link</code>实现外链<code>css</code>文件</li></ul><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">link</span> <span class="attr">rel</span>=<span class="string">&quot;stylesheet&quot;</span> <span class="attr">href</span>=<span class="string">&quot;style.css&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="CSS选择器那些事儿"><a href="#CSS选择器那些事儿" class="headerlink" title="CSS选择器那些事儿"></a>CSS选择器那些事儿</h2><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">ul</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">a</span> <span class="attr">href</span>=<span class="string">index.html</span>&gt;</span>Home<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">a</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">a</span> <span class="attr">href</span>=<span class="string">locations.html</span>&gt;</span>Locations<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">a</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">a</span> <span class="attr">href</span>=<span class="string">contact.html</span>&gt;</span>Contact<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">a</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">ul</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">section</span> <span class="attr">id</span>=<span class="string">&quot;frank&quot;</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">&quot;feature-box sales&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span>section a<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span>section b<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span>section c<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">section</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>此时有多种类选择器玩法</li></ul><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">.feature-box &#123;</span><br><span class="line">xxx;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">.feature-box div &#123;</span><br><span class="line">xxx;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">.feature-box.sales div &#123;</span><br><span class="line">xxx;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">#frank &#123;</span><br><span class="line">xxx;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">li:first-child &#123;</span><br><span class="line">xxx;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>超链接移入后改变效果</li></ul><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">a &#123;</span><br><span class="line">text-decoration: none;</span><br><span class="line">color: gray;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">a:hover &#123;</span><br><span class="line">text-decoration: underline;</span><br><span class="line">color: white;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="搭建第一个语义化标签"><a href="#搭建第一个语义化标签" class="headerlink" title="搭建第一个语义化标签"></a>搭建第一个语义化标签</h2><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">header</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">nav</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">ul</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">&quot;logo&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">a</span> <span class="attr">href</span>=<span class="string">&quot;index.html&quot;</span>&gt;</span>Logo<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">a</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">ul</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">nav</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">header</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">section</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">&quot;features&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">figure</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">img</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">&quot;images/breads.jpg&quot;</span> <span class="attr">alt</span>=<span class="string">&quot;amazing fresh baked bread&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">figcaption</span>&gt;</span>Fresh Baked Bread<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">figcaption</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">figure</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">figure</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">img</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">&quot;images/coffee.jpg&quot;</span> <span class="attr">alt</span>=<span class="string">&quot;amazing fresh coffee&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">figcaption</span>&gt;</span>Home Roasted Coffee<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">figcaption</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">figure</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">section</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">style</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="css">    <span class="selector-tag">header</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="css">        <span class="attribute">background-color</span>: black;<span class="comment">/*预加载时显示的一个背景图*/</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="css">        <span class="attribute">background-image</span>: <span class="built_in">url</span>(<span class="string">&quot;images/hero.jpg&quot;</span>);</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="css">        <span class="attribute">background-size</span>: <span class="number">100%</span>;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="css">        <span class="attribute">height</span>: <span class="number">400px</span>;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="css">        <span class="attribute">padding</span>: <span class="number">20px</span>;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="css">        <span class="attribute">text-align</span>: center;<span class="comment">/*文本对齐方式：居中*/</span></span></span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line"><span class="css">    <span class="selector-tag">header</span> <span class="selector-tag">a</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="css">        <span class="attribute">color</span>: white;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="css">        <span class="attribute">text-decoration</span>: none;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="css">        <span class="attribute">text-transform</span>: uppercase;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="css">        <span class="attribute">margin-top</span>: <span class="number">40px</span>;</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line"><span class="css">    <span class="selector-tag">header</span> <span class="selector-class">.logo</span> <span class="selector-tag">a</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="css">        <span class="attribute">background-image</span>: <span class="built_in">url</span>(<span class="string">&quot;images/logo/png&quot;</span>);</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="css">        <span class="attribute">background-size</span>: <span class="number">300px</span>;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="css">        <span class="attribute">background-repeat</span>: no-repeat;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="css">        <span class="attribute">display</span>: inline-block;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="css">        <span class="attribute">height</span>: <span class="number">80px</span>;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="css">        <span class="attribute">text-indent</span>: -<span class="number">99999px</span>;<span class="comment">/*文本缩进*/</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="css">        <span class="attribute">top</span>: -<span class="number">40px</span>;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="css">        <span class="attribute">width</span>: <span class="number">30px</span>;</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    .features &#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="css">        <span class="attribute">background</span>: white;</span></span